headline: New research identifies construction skilled labor gap as a major barrier to post-disaster rebuilding
summary: One year after the devastating Los Angeles wildfires, new research released today by The Home Depot Foundation and Morning Consult highlights a growing tension in disaster recovery: even when funding is available, skilled labor often is not.
